text: Talina Gantenbein (born 18 August 1998) is a Swiss freestyle skier. She competed in the 2018 Winter Olympics, in ski cross. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss female freestyle skiers Category:Olympic freestyle skiers of Switzerland Category:Freestyle skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Competitors at the 2016 Winter Youth Olympics Category:Youth Olympic gold medalists for Switzerland
